quote>bc都係漢奸</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你咪港奸囉五毛狗</span></blockquote><br />\n香港自古而來係中國一部分，支持中國又有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自古以來蒙古都係中國一部分<br />\n海參威又係，幾時拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五毛敢唔敢回答下呢個問題,老共敢拎返我第一個認做中国人"},{"pid":"bd7a3a416c32ca2d0128e30d8cc1c356c7905a70","tid":495211,"uid":63669,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bc都係漢奸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好過有啲人想做都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaf987996c1a8a0de6170e565ca33f08de8da46","tid":495211,"uid":60686,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"有BC 都唔易係英國搵工。<br />\n利：CPA"},{"pid":"c57573ad3e807ed7808582b5f7927945dd5b57fa","tid":495211,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>基本上英美加澳護照先鍾意留係香港<br />\n有咩事即走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇外國護照個堆先想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有護照個班先會叫你愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偏偏就有班低等人口真心膠真係同你擁護大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e5bc48581af91ec63139db7f4d74420a828826","tid":495211,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T20:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有BC 都唔易係英國搵工。<br />\n利：CPA</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAt lease you have a professional qualification and British Citizenship which means that you do not need to get a visa in order to get a job in the UK. All you need to do is to get a National Insurance Number once you are in the UK - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/apply-national-insurance-number\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fapply-national-insurance-number&d=cz0NtoQHsL2naZ4LrITYlsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=77a264c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/apply-national-insurance-number</a><br />\n<br />\nHave a look at the link below for some information on how you can practice in England and Wales - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.icaew.com/en/membership/becoming-a-member/members-of-other-bodies/members-of-other-bodies-a-z/hkicpa-members-join-icaew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.icaew.com%2Fen%2Fmembership%2Fbecoming-a-member%2Fmembers-of-other-bodies%2Fmembers-of-other-bodies-a-z%2Fhkicpa-members-join-icaew&d=cz0NtoQHsL2naZ4LrITYlsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4fc81193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.icaew.com/en/membership/becoming-a-member/members-of-other-bodies/members-of-other-bodies-a-z/hkicpa-members-join-icaew</a><br />\n<br />\nPlease note that if you are a British Citizen by descent (for example you were not born or naturalised in the UK), your children born outside of the UK cannot automatically get British Citizenship via you."},{"pid":"aa833087f7cc1f9069be9e6ff863083c95953aae","tid":495211,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T20:07:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69f7382bbc09acf03e1d3671e5d8160e8b3b1774","tid":495211,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T20:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>bc都係漢奸</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你咪港奸囉五毛狗</span></blockquote><br />\n香港自古而來係中國一部分，支持中國又有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n你呢d鼓吹講毒思想，唯恐天下不亂既人先叫做港奸<br />\n你出街問下有幾多人好似你咁，想香港咁鬼亂架</blockquote><br />\n波台假膠死撚開啦"},{"pid":"c7846af1038f036511b3338f2b4c016573f8e244","tid":495211,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislik